{"tid":2074258,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"濫捕無後果 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-06-22T03:28:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-22T08:52:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"b334c9ebd5bf2f442638ee24f9a4add2883202e1","tid":2074258,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:28:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200622/20941718/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200622%2F20941718%2F&d=oSWSjOI%2Bg%2Fd3CLQu9eb0F8hAN7np5IU55thb9t6%2Bojg%3D&h=b5e51aaa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200622%2F20941718%2F&h=bc206e40\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200622/20941718/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n濫捕無後果 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200622/large/1592724248_73cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200622%2Flarge%2F1592724248_73cc.jpg&h=6106f9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n22歲任職巿場推廣員女子，。。。。。，上月被控襲警罪。<br />\n<br />\n不過，一段來自理大校園的閉路電視清晰拍下全過程，顯示涉案士沙當時在被告身後，用手肘撞擊被告，隨後自己跌倒，倒地之後士沙用警棍指向被告。整個過程中被告沒有任何動作。結果，控方甫開庭便決定撤控。<br />\n<br />\n獲撤控的女被告在庭外與母親相擁，激動流淚，。。。。。。，但苦於沒有證人目擊，也沒有被閉路電視拍到，而坐了冤獄的？<br />\n<br />\n案件中濫捕濫告的警察需要承擔責任嗎？好像沒有。會面對法律後果嗎？好像不會。如果濫告濫捕不用承擔任何責任和後果，警察會引以為鑑嗎？當然不會。如果濫捕濫告不用承擔任何責任和後果，警察會繼續濫捕濫告嗎？當然會。這是正常邏輯吧？<br />\n<br />\n同一日被控襲警罪的29歲小學教師運氣就差得多了，被告因駕車時車速太慢被截查，被控踢警長。現場三位警員之中，有兩位聲稱看不到被告施襲。裁判官卻以「三警員證供不一，顯示各人沒有夾口供」而裁定被告罪名成立，明言必定判監。該名小學教師現獲高院保釋候判，繼續承受難以想像的壓力。 <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"b1f1b62a7663b068baedcb06777492affb5fbb2e","tid":2074258,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:30:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3cdd3768899eaf87311ff03ad7b9fe24b9bee66","tid":2074258,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:30:44.000Z","msg":"沙展仆落地 屈女生襲警 網片成鐵證撤控<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2071488\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2071488</a>"},{"pid":"a6009598620c7081ca0de3cbc6130541b05d8530","tid":2074258,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:31:10.000Z","msg":"自己仆倒 誣告女子襲警  沙展涉礙司法公正 大狀：律政司應促警查<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2073137\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2073137</a>"},{"pid":"941d6070be9c08965ad2e971725971717c2ca1dc","tid":2074258,"uid":204539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:34:52.000Z","msg":"香港警察 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa960cd3ef7c4754af86a4403dbac231055a0aad","tid":2074258,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:37:58.000Z","msg":"老屈亂告都無後果"},{"pid":"5943ab284aceb1dbe985b49e5c217a2d05b14730","tid":2074258,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:40:32.000Z","msg":"咁人地又真係跟足情序做野,<br />\n唔通覺得有可疑都唔拉得咩?<br />\n<br />\n即係醫生懷疑你想作病,<br />\n都會叫你啪幾粒維他命丸<br />\n你又告醫生濫開藥?"},{"pid":"1fe350ab7f6b51563e1eeef44985bd36d9613443","tid":2074258,"uid":294121,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-22T03:53:56.000Z","msg":"以前日本皇軍捉埋你去姦添<br />\n而家濫捕算得d咩😹"},{"pid":"07019e8c46ba31c8d0f6f74d717c001fdd286e50","tid":2074258,"uid":266382,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5943ab284aceb1dbe985b49e5c217a2d05b14730","tid":2074258,"uid":124277,"like":0,"dis